@startuml
[*] --> CheckingStartup : power on
CheckingStartup --> ReadyToUse : everything fine (nothing)
ReadyToUse --> ReadyToUse : reset (reset button), activate (activation command), turn off (shutdown command)
ReadyToUse --> ActivatedMonitoring : activated (activate command)
ActivatedMonitoring --> Alarming : sensor triggered (sensor alert)
Alarming --> Normal : password entered (password entered) or time ends (timeout)
Normal --> [*] : power off
@enduml
